  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb0\u0bc2. 75 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vimal against Rs. 75 million asset accumulation case adjourned",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo High Court adjourned the case centered on the crime report filed by the Bribery Corruption Commission against the former Minister Wimal Weerawansa in the Colombo High Court regarding the acquisition of property through illegal means, and the date of the 'pre trial conference' to the upcoming 13th of September.",
        "Accordingly, it will be examined in the pre-trial meeting on September 13 whether sufficient evidence and testimony have been submitted to proceed with the case.",
        "This asset accumulation case has been filed in relation to 75 million rupees of money and assets that were added in a way that the means of earning could not be disclosed during the period when Vimal Weerawansa was the minister, i.e. between 1st January 2009 and 31st December 2014.",
        "In this regard, the Bribery Corruption Commission has laid 26 charges against Vimal and submitted a list of 32 witnesses, 13 documents and 40 pieces of evidence in the court to prove them.",
        "It is to be noted that the said properties which are said to have been added illegally by Vimal include house, vehicles and money."
      ],
